txt.en: Amid the wreckage along the road to Middlemead, you have discovered a crate of crops from Kingstead that withstood the Uruk assault. If more crates remain intact, such supplies would be of great value to the warriors of Entwade in their preparation for the coming assault.
You must gather more crates of crops before returning to Entwade.
You have recovered many crates of Kingstead crops and should now prepare to return them to Entwade.
Uruks of the White Hand encroach ever closer on the settlements of Kingstead, aiming to starve or slay any in their path.

Crates of Kingstead crops can be found along the road to Middlemead in eastern Kingstead.\n\nYou have discovered a crate of crops that has survived the Uruk onslaught. You should recover as many as you can to aid the forces at Entwade.
You have recovered many of the crops pillaged by the Uruks near Entwade. With these renewed supplies, Entwade will have the rations necessary to hold through the impending assault.
